name: Attribute_setKeyTest
description: Unit tests for the setKey method in the Attribute class.

test_cases.name: testSetKeyWithValidKey
test_cases.description: Tests setting a valid key in the Attribute and verifies the key and value in the parent Attributes.

test_cases.name: testSetKeyWithEmptyParent
test_cases.description: Tests setting a key in the Attribute when the parent is null.

test_cases.name: testSetKeyWithNullKey
test_cases.description: Tests setting a null key in the Attribute and expects an IllegalArgumentException.

test_cases.name: testSetKeyWithEmptyKey
test_cases.description: Tests setting an empty key in the Attribute and expects an IllegalArgumentException.

test_cases.name: testSetKeyWithWhitespaceKey
test_cases.description: Tests setting a key with leading and trailing whitespace in the Attribute and verifies the key and value in the parent Attributes.

test_cases.name: testSetKeyWithExistingKeyInParent
test_cases.description: Tests setting a key in the Attribute that already exists in the parent Attributes and verifies the key and value in the parent Attributes.

test_cases.name: testSetKeyWithRangeTracking
test_cases.description: Tests setting a key in the Attribute with range tracking and verifies the key and value in the parent Attributes.
